    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224600/extras/7be6cd90a43436e442ccd57a57131fa8.poster.avif?t=1758432322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224600/extras/7be6cd90a43436e442ccd57a57131fa8.webm?t=1758432322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224600/extras/7be6cd90a43436e442ccd57a57131fa8.mp4?t=1758432322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不记得自己到底是谁。但现在你要模仿她的行动，学习她说话的口吻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Am I Nima》将带你进入妮玛支离破碎的精神世界。你被母亲锁在昏暗的地下室中，如果想要逃离这里，就需要通过她的多道考验、调查那些似曾相识的房间……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最初你毫无头绪，但随着探索深入，你从破旧的布娃娃、上锁的抽屉、字迹潦草的旧纸条等事物中剥离出相关的词语和概念，它们帮助你构建对周遭世界的理解，你也可以用它们来引导你与母亲的对话。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224600/extras/80d6c56c9460d02559e5fc99d4dcdc2c.poster.avif?t=1758432322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224600/extras/80d6c56c9460d02559e5fc99d4dcdc2c.webm?t=1758432322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224600/extras/80d6c56c9460d02559e5fc99d4dcdc2c.mp4?t=1758432322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，光是获取信息还不够，你必须积极地组合妮玛脑海中的词语，尝试不同的搭配，挖掘更深层的含义，从而触及那些被尘封的记忆。有些词语组合如火光乍现，使你猛然顿悟，过去的片段如潮水般涌现；还有一些词语组合则会扭曲你的认知，揭示出那些令人不安的矛盾。你会开始逐渐怀疑：你自以为了解的一切，是否真的是那样？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索越深，疑问越多：母亲为何将你锁在地下室？这些考验背后有何意图？而你自己……究竟是不是妮玛？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前游戏仅Steam页面进行了翻译，游戏内暂时只提供英文版本。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224600/extras/ef2ca43f1e06f405d83e4cf319285733.poster.avif?t=1758432322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224600/extras/ef2ca43f1e06f405d83e4cf319285733.webm?t=1758432322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224600/extras/ef2ca43f1e06f405d83e4cf319285733.mp4?t=1758432322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
